name: VIDEO: Gillespie Field Hosts Firefighting Helicopters
description: The County of San Diego is hosting military firefighting helicopters at Gillespie Field to help fight the Valley Fire.

affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent:
The County of San Diego is hosting military firefighting helicopters at Gillespie Field to help fight the Valley Fire.
Gillespie Field’s two other runways remain open to the public.
